name: __EPlaneConstraintAxisSetting
doc:
Setting that controls behavior when movement is restricted to a 2D plane defined by a specific axis/normal,
so that movement along the locked axis is not be possible.

Custom: Lock movement to a user-defined axis.
X: Lock movement in the X axis.
Y: Lock movement in the Y axis.
Z: Lock movement in the Z axis.
UseGlobalPhysicsSetting: Use the global physics project setting.
